        <fw type="pageNum">Letter from R. O. Reynolds to Mississippi Governor John M. Stone; May 19, 1877</fw>
          <p corresp='TTP34100077P0' xml:id='OTP34100077P0'><rs ref='#S103493'>L. E. Houston</rs> [gap] <rs ref='#S32023295'>R. O. Reynolds</rs>.
