<p corresp='TTP34100077P1' xml:id='OTP34100077P1'><rs ref='#S32138856'><b>Houston &amp; Reynolds,</b><lb/>
ATTORNEYS AND COUNSELORS AT LAW</rs>,<lb/>
<hr/>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34100077P2' xml:id='OTP34100077P2'><hi rend='italic'><rs ref='#S63400'>Aberdeen, Miss.</rs></hi> May 19 <hi rend='italic'>187</hi>7
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34100077P3' xml:id='OTP34100077P3'>I will recommend the payment of $200 to any persons, who will return to their parents the children alleged to have been <rs ref='#S72342'>kidnaped</rs> from the <rs ref='#S32067297'>Coleman</rs> place &amp; carried to <rs ref='#S63022'>Tenn.</rs> The recommendation to the Gov of the State.
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34100077P4' xml:id='OTP34100077P4'>R. O. Reynolds
</p>


        </div>
